---
title: Southwestern Beef Tacos with Bell Pepper, Lime Crema, and Pepper Jack Cheese
description: What do we want from a taco? We want meat seasoned in warm and smoky spices. We want it to rain cheese, sour cream, jalapeño, and lime. We want the tortilla to exhale steam as we’re reaching in for a big bite. Luckily, these beef and bell pepper bad boys are giving us all of that, making this a bona fide taco-night triumph.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwestern-beef-tacos-e63d936e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/southwestern-beef-tacos-5c7978b1c445fa2dfd25d7a2-8bd67df6.pdf
